Stanley J. CATERBONE, Petitioner
v.
LANCASTER CITY BUREAU OF POLICE, et al.
No. 19-5228
Supreme Court of the United States.
October 7, 2019
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
